{"tid":1324373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（緊急呼籲）連登仔同我聽住","createTime":"2019-07-16T14:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T04:04:06.000Z","uid":56682,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a01735e53461ed5e57e123bb7fbc1c31676bcde0","tid":1324373,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:09:05.000Z","msg":"【 速報】《中英聯合聲明》眾籌備戰情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324214</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n該入咗嚟嘅連登仔同我聽住<br />\n<br />\n我要你哋依家即刻每人都去申請一個reddit帳號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當英國登咗嗰篇新聞出咗街之後， 你就即刻搵人去reddit開post <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後每個人都要將個post up上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然可能幫唔到好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但<br />\n<br />\n星星之火，可以燎原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且難保日後有其他事要引起外國網民關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://www.reddit.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=fb8d4afe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reddit.com</a>"},{"pid":"8f006daac454050eb75989a19ae634c7134bf988","tid":1324373,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:09:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fc434595de914efe44947e5d300556f3eb2c78f